                            <comment id="14472076" author="paulk" created="Tue, 22 Nov 2011 23:37:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The generated source for the underlying proxy object which works on 1.8.1 but fails from 1.8.2 is the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;URLConnection_groovyProxy &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; java.net.URLConnection {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; closureMap
    URLConnection_groovyProxy(map, args) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;super&lt;/span&gt;(*args)
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.closureMap = map
    }
    void connect() { &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; UnsupportedOperationException()    }
}
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; URLConnection_groovyProxy(map, constructorArgs)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14472131" author="melix" created="Wed, 23 Nov 2011 11:17:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bisecting leads to the following commit:&lt;/p&gt;
